      <title>数据好坏参半后，债券交易员对美联储的态度略微乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/treasury-yields-steady-amid-mixed-data-on-growth-and-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列美国经济数据显示经济增长强于预期且物价压力持续消退之后，债券交易商预计美联储今年降息幅度将略大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/treasury-yields-steady-amid-mixed-data-on-growth-and-inflation</guid>
