    <item>
      <title>信贷交易员正在利用违约掉期来对冲利率押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/credit-traders-are-using-default-swaps-to-hedge-their-bets-on-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村资产管理公司(Nomura Asset Management)的理查德·霍奇斯(Richard Hodges)年初购买了信用违约掉期产品，担心降息押注变得过于激进。当保护成本增加时，他减少了对冲，现在准备再次介入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/credit-traders-are-using-default-swaps-to-hedge-their-bets-on-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GDP之后股市将再创新高：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美联储仍维持高利率提振了企业盈利前景，但数据显示经济仍具弹性，股市上涨至另一个历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
